* Iron Raptor took the tube and knife from Prowl without even looking up, 
her optics fixed on the wound in Dinobot's chest and her thoughts on how she 
was going to do this.
However, she heard his words.*

" I could use some suction to get rid of the mech-fluid that might pool and 
abstruct my view of what I'm doing."

* And with that she simply reached towards the warriors chest wound with the 
knife, simply looking at the blade before she sank it into the wound and cut 
the metal down towards his stomack.
It was a bit hard and she had to put a bit of pressure behind it, but the 
transmetal 2 metal began to give way and the wound became larger.
Iron Raptor looked down at her work, opening the wound a bit and slightly 
felt relieved at what she saw next, but a bit perplexed as well.
There was Dinobots' lungs and she could clearly see the small rip that was 
in it, but she realized that maybe this has to be done a certain way.
But there wasn't time to think about that now, she had to get to work before 
the time was up...or he'd die!
She sighes a but, trying to at least relax a little, but with the clock 
running against her, it was almost impossable.*

" I need something to close this rip in his lung, maybe welding equipment, 
something that'll ment TM2 armor."


* But then her mind suddenly brought up a very important factorl, where in 
the pit was Feline? SHE was the one who was supposed to be doing this!
And here she was, Iron Raptoe, programed to fight but no common sense on how 
to fix a bot by hand. She was doing everything by common sense and simple 
know how.*
